  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为供应链管理系统设计一个完整的架构图。首先，最外层应该有一个Nginx负载均衡器作为流量入口，所有外部请求都经过这里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Load Balancer - Nginx"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Nginx作为统一入口。那它下游直接连到各个服务，还是需要先经过一个API网关层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Load Balancer - Nginx"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要API网关，我们用的是AWS API Gateway。这样Nginx通过HTTP/HTTPS把流量转发给网关，网关再做路由分发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Load Balancer - Nginx",
        "API Gateway - AWS API Gateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了Nginx到AWS API Gateway的连接，标注为HTTP/HTTPS。现在需要设计网关后面的服务层吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Load Balancer - Nginx",
        "API Gateway - AWS API Gateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，服务层有四个核心服务。首先是认证服务，用JWT和OAuth 2.0实现，所有请求都要先经过它验证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Authentication Service - JWT, OAuth 2.0"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "认证服务通过REST API与网关交互，我记下了。其他三个服务是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API Gateway - AWS API Gateway",
        "Authentication Service - JWT, OAuth 2.0"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第二个是区块链服务，基于以太坊做智能合约交互；第三个是供应链管理服务，这是业务核心；第四个是通知服务，用AWS SNS和Twilio发消息。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Blockchain Service - Ethereum",
        "Supply Chain Management Service",
        "Notification Service - AWS SNS, Twilio"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加这三个服务，并且把API Gateway到认证服务、供应链服务、通知服务的连接都用REST API标注好了。区块链服务不需要直连网关吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API Gateway - AWS API Gateway",
        "Authentication Service - JWT, OAuth 2.0",
        "Supply Chain Management Service",
        "Notification Service - AWS SNS, Twilio"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "区块链服务不直接暴露给网关，它只跟供应链服务交互。供应链服务通过智能合约调用区块链，这样更安全。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Blockchain Service - Ethereum",
        "Supply Chain Management Service"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解了，我画了一条从供应链服务到区块链服务的线，标注为Smart Contract Interaction。供应链服务还需要连接数据层吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Supply Chain Management Service",
        "Blockchain Service - Ethereum"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要，主数据库用PostgreSQL，供应链服务通过SQL读写数据。另外还要加一个Redis缓存层，做热点数据加速。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PostgreSQL Database - PostgreSQL",
        "Cache - Redis"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加PostgreSQL和Redis，供应链服务到数据库标注SQL，到缓存标注Cache Lookup。还有外部依赖吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Supply Chain Management Service",
        "PostgreSQL Database - PostgreSQL",
        "Cache - Redis"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有，我们需要对接第三方数据API，比如物流信息、汇率这些。供应链服务和通知服务都要调用外部API。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "External Data API - Third-party APIs",
