      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "添加了External Data API节点。供应链服务到外部API是Data Fetch，通知服务到外部API是SMS/Email Notification。这样连接关系都画完了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "External Data API - Third-party APIs",
        "Supply Chain Management Service",
        "Notification Service - AWS SNS, Twilio"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "现在需要给不同层级上色区分。Nginx用浅蓝色表示用户界面层，API Gateway用紫色表示API层，四个核心服务用绿色，数据库用橙色，缓存用粉色，外部API用浅绿色。",
      "elements_involved": [
